title: Foldable chess board
description:
Chess that goes with you – always ready to play!
Compact and portable for any pocket or bag – your newest game on the move.
Fun and interactive: perfect for coffee, travel, or a quick game with a friend.
Aesthetic and practical – each piece is designed to make playing simple and stylish.

title: Heart-shaped decorative box
description: The heart-shaped decorative box, with a lid adorned with finely engraved roses, is the perfect blend of aesthetics and functionality. Designed with attention to detail, it is the ideal place for your most precious items or a perfect gift for a special person.

title: Formula 1 tracks poster 2025
description:
'Racing Tracks 2025' – a 3D poster that brings the world of Formula 1 to life.
Experience the dynamics of Formula 1 with this unique 3D poster featuring all 24 tracks from the 2025 season. Designed with attention to detail, this poster is ideal for motorsport fans who want to decorate their space with style.

title: Katana sword
description:
'When the world is at peace, a gentleman keeps his sword by his side' – Wu Tsu.
This katana sword is perfect for anyone who wants to express their unique style. Whether you are a fan of samurai culture, a cosplay enthusiast, or just want to add some authenticity to your space, this katana is the perfect choice.

title: Melting Grim Reaper
description: Melting Grim Reaper is an artistic 3D ornament that combines the symbolism of the Grim Reaper with a surreal melting effect. Ideal for collectors and fans of themed decorations.

title: Travel box - GoPro
description: Protect your GoPro camera wherever you go with our compact and durable Travel Box. Designed to protect your GoPro from impacts, dust, and moisture – wherever the road takes you. Style, protection, and security in one.

title: Helmet holder 1
description: Modern and sturdy design that keeps your helmet safe and elegantly displayed. Easy to mount, durable for everyday use, and perfect for garages, offices, or rooms of true bikers. Organize your space and turn your helmet into part of the decor.

title: Helmet holder 2
description: Modern and sturdy design that keeps your helmet safe and elegantly displayed. Easy to mount, durable for everyday use, and perfect for garages, offices, or rooms of true bikers. Organize your space and turn your helmet into part of the decor.

title: 3D printed Christmas tree with LED tealight
description: 3D printed Christmas tree with LED tealight – a gentle light that beautifies the festive atmosphere. With its fine lines and warm glow, it brings a festive feeling to every corner of the home. Perfect for the holiday table, a quiet evening with loved ones, or as a small heartfelt gift.

title: SD card holder - Spartan
description: 3D printed SD card holder in the shape of a Spartan – a powerful design for your small but important data. Precisely made for safe storage and easy access to your cards, while also serving as a striking decoration for your desk.

title: Airplane - General Dynamics F-16
description: 3D printed model of the legendary General Dynamics F-16 – a symbol of speed, agility, and precision. Finely crafted to capture the silhouette and dynamics of one of the most recognizable fighters in the world. Perfect as a decoration for aviation enthusiasts.

title: Apple phone + watch charging station
description: Charging station for iPhone and Apple Watch – an elegant solution for order and style. Designed to fit your devices perfectly, this station provides safe and organized charging while bringing a modern look to your desk or nightstand.

title: Monica's peephole door frame
description: 3D printed Monica’s Peephole Door Frame – straight from the door of the most famous apartment in New York! A faithful replica of the frame from Friends, this detail brings nostalgia and cheer to any home. Perfect gift for true fans of the series or a unique ornament for your door.

title: Decorative box with ribbon
description: Decorative box with ribbon – a small but striking detail that makes every occasion special. Elegantly crafted with precise lines, perfect for packing small gifts, jewelry, or symbolic surprises.

title: Espresso accessories organizer
description: Specially designed for neat storage of portafilter (51mm to 53mm), tamper, and other necessary tools, this organizer brings order and a professional look next to the coffee machine. Compact, durable, and stylish – perfect for true espresso lovers.

title: Storage box
description: Custom printed box – designed exactly to your needs and taste. Choose size, shape, and style, and we will make it with precision and quality. Perfect for storage or packaging – a unique solution that combines practicality with personalized design.

title: Controller holder - rock
description: Display your controller like a true trophy – on a 3D printed holder in the shape of a rock. With a natural look and stable base, this holder keeps your controller safe and stylish, while adding a unique decorative accent to your gaming space.

title: Controller holder - spikes
description: Keep your controller as if in a battle arena – on a 3D printed holder in the shape of spikes. The impressive, sharp design not only provides stability and safety, but also adds a powerful visual effect to your gaming setup.

title: Controller holder - PlayStation
description: Gamers know – the joystick deserves a throne! Our 3D holder is the perfect place for your PlayStation controller. Style + order in one!

title: Decorative wine holder
description: With a modern and refined design, this holder turns every bottle into part of the decor. Perfect for dining rooms, kitchens, or gifts, it brings a touch of elegance and highlights wine as a true pleasure.

title: Meditating reaper LED candle holder
description: When silence speaks – 'Meditating Reaper'. The image of the reaper in a meditative pose brings a unique balance between darkness and calm. The light creates a warm, yet mystical atmosphere – a perfect piece for lovers of unusual and striking decor.

title: Chin mount for action camera
description: Designed for mounting on the front of the helmet, this holder provides a central perspective and firm attachment without vibrations. Made of durable material, resistant to impacts and weather conditions – ideal for bikers, MTB riders, and anyone who wants to record adventures with maximum clarity.

title: LED tealight holder - Snowflake
description: The elegant snowflake design and precise craftsmanship turn every LED tealight into a warm decorative accent. Perfect for festive evenings, winter decorations, or as a small gift that brings joy and light.

title: Elegant LED tealight holder
description: Created to highlight the light and warmth of the tealight, this holder brings subtle aesthetics to any setting. Perfect as a stylish accent in a modern home.

title: Grinch - door decoration
description: 3D printed Grinch door decoration – festive mischief with the recognizable face of the most beloved holiday anti-hero. With its legendary expression and vivid details, this ornament brings humor and playful spirit to the home.

title: Decoration - pointe shoes
description: Grace in miniature – 3D decoration with pointe shoes for a ballerina. With refined details and gentle lines, this ornament captures the beauty of ballet and is perfect for stage lovers, dancers, or as a unique gift that brings elegance and inspiration.

title: Decoration - ballerina
description: Delicacy in motion – a ballerina ornament that conveys the quiet magic of ballet. With its refined craftsmanship, it brings harmony and style to any space. Ideal choice for ballet lovers and as a gift that speaks with elegance.

title: Christmas light-up ornament
description: Christmas light-up ornament – the magic of the holidays in one piece. With refined design and warm lighting, this ornament creates a pleasant and festive atmosphere at home. Perfect for decoration that brings light, joy, and holiday spirit.

title: Christmas ornament - Merry Christmas
description: Festive welcome with the 3D printed 'Merry Christmas' ornament for door or wall. With festive shine, this ornament brings warmth and joy to the space, creating a celebratory atmosphere from the first glance. Perfect for rounding off Christmas decorations and delighting guests.

title: Christmas baubles
description: Add magic to the holidays with 3D printed baubles. Unique design and precise craftsmanship – perfect for the tree or festive arrangement. Baubles can be bought individually or as a set.

title: Christmas cookie cutters
description: Add festive magic to the kitchen – with 3D printed Christmas cookie cutters. Creative shapes and precise craftsmanship for cookies that look beautiful and bring festive joy.

title: Standing Christmas lamp
description: Warm festive glow – standing Christmas lamp with LED bulb. The gentle design and pleasant lighting bring magic to every corner of the home, turning festive evenings into warm memories.

title: Vinyl record holder
description: Where music rests – 3D printed vinyl record holder. With a unique design and sturdy construction, it keeps your favorite albums neatly and proudly displayed, turning your music collection into part of the decor.

title: Mini drum set
description: Rhythm in miniature – 3D printed mini drum set. With finely crafted details and realistic appearance, this mini set is perfect decor for music lovers, collectors, or as a unique gift that brings musical spirit into the space.

title: MotoGP race tracks poster
description: MotoGP Race Tracks poster – the tracks that write the history of speed. With precisely depicted contours of legendary MotoGP tracks, this poster is perfect for motorsport fans. Minimalist and stylish design that will enrich any wall and bring racing spirit to your space.

title: Moving dragon
description: The magic of the dragon in your palm – 3D printed moving model. With a segmented design that allows flexible and realistic movement, this dragon is a perfect blend of fantasy and precision.

title: Harry Potter Hermione Granger's wand
description: The magic of Hermione in your hands – 3D printed replica of her legendary wand, with a stand for proud display. Made with precision and attention to every detail, this piece brings a part of the Harry Potter world directly into your home. Perfect for collectors and fans who want magic always within reach.

title: Honeycomb - key holder/keychain holder
description: Honeycomb key and keychain holder – inspired by nature. With a hexagonal structure like a honeycomb, this modern holder provides practical and organized storage for keys. Ideal for hallway, office, or workspace.

title: Heart-shaped candle holder
description: Gentle glow in the shape of love – heart-shaped candle holder. This sweet decor piece brings joy and tenderness to every corner of the home. Also ideal as a gift that radiates love.

title: Rose-shaped ring box
description: Ring box in the shape of a rose – a symbol of love and elegance. The gently shaped petals hide the most beautiful declaration of love, turning the moment into a unique story. This box turns the act of giving into an unforgettable moment.

title: Heart-shaped decorative box
description: A heart that keeps memories – decorative box with a romantic shape. Gently crafted and refined, perfect for storing jewelry, small souvenirs, or your dearest memories.

title: Cute couple in love - ornament
description: The moment when hearts meet – 3D ornament - Cute Couple in Love. Gently shaped and full of emotion, this ornament conveys the warmth of love and closeness. Perfect choice for a gift that will decorate your story.

title: Forever roses
description: For her, a rose that lasts forever. With delicately shaped petals and an elegant silhouette, this rose keeps its beauty forever. The perfect way to give attention and tenderness.

title: Rose with inscription 'I love you'
description: A rose that whispers I Love You – 3D flower full of tenderness. With sweet details and warm charm, this rose is the perfect symbol of attention and love. A gift that will warm the heart of your loved one, mother, or someone who means everything to you.

title: Vase
description: Where elegance gently embraces modern design – 3D printed vase that captivates at first glance. With gracefully shaped lines and a refined silhouette, it brings subtle charm and sophisticated beauty to any space. Perfect for highlighting the freshness and color of any flower, turning your home into a place filled with style and warmth.

title: Decorative box with locking key
description: A small chest full of magic and charm. With elegant lines and a romantic shape, this chest is the perfect place for storing small treasures and precious memories. A gift that captivates with beauty and brings joy every time it is opened.

title: Car visor glasses holder
description: Practical glasses holder for car visor – order and security within reach. Designed for easy attachment to the visor, this holder keeps your glasses safe, protected from scratches, and always at hand.

title: Key and heart keychains
description: The key to your heart – a set of personalized keychains for you and your loved one. The heart and key come together in a symbol of love and closeness, and the personalized details make your story unique.
